    "title": "Chromatin!",
    "description": "&quot;Identity is not an object; it is a process with addresses for all the different directions and dimensions in which it moves, and so it cannot so easily be fixed with a single number.&quot;\n\n&quot;1 + 1 = 1&quot;\n\n&quot;The question &quot;What is Life?&quot; is... a linguistic trap. To answer according to the rules of grammar, we must supply a noun, a thing. But life on Earth is more like a verb. It repairs, maintains, re-creates, and outdoes itself.&quot;\n\n--Lynn Margulis",
